title: Adobe Photoshop CS3 Extended Portable
description:
---Photoshop CS3---

Photoshop CS3 Extended includes all of the same features as Photoshop CS3 
but adds a brand-new set of tools and capabilities for the integration of 
3-D models, video and animation, and image measurement and analysis.

In CS3, Adobe did a very good job of making interface improvements without 
moving too far away from the familiar. Most of the new elements unique to 
Photoshop Extended are well integrated into the standard Photoshop and 
accessed from familiar tools such as the Layers panel or various menus.
3-D compositing and texture editing.
